settings.description: In Oct. 2021, I made a level called "Woody Purple Fiends," but due to a glitch, I changed the title by "Black Killer Holes." Now there's a game crash there, so I did some cleanup to fix everything.
A fortress filled with interesting contraptions Bowser threw in.
